							<li>To disable cookies, move the slider to the top</li>
							<li>There are various levels of cookie enablement and disablement in Internet Explorer. For more information on other cookie settings offered in Internet Explorer, refer to the following page from Microsoft: <a href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-GB/windows-vista/Block-or-allow-cookies">http://windows.microsoft.com/en-GB/windows-vista/Block-or-allow-cookies</a></li>
						</ul>
